data.description:
Nestled in a quiet community, this patio home is just 3-5 minutes from shopping and restaurants. This highly sought after end unit features 2 full bathrooms with an en suite in the Primary. Enjoy an open floor plan with wood floors, custom kitchen w/granite countertops, tray ceilings in the LR, Primary, and Sunroom. A private fenced-in patio is included at the end of the unit. All kitchen appliances included. Turnkey/move-in ready!
Recent upgrades include: *All new carpet
*All new two-tone paint
*All new window blinds
*All new ceiling fans w/light kits
*All new smoke alarms
*2 full bathrooms w/en suite in Primary
*Highly sought after end unit w/Sunroom
*Wood floors in main area of open floor plan
*Custom kitchen with granite countertops
*Tray ceilings in LR, Primary, and Sunroom
